<title>ḥbẗ qlbk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- nạym wʿywnk ḥạrsạny ʿạysẖ wdrạʿk sạndạny
 ạ̹yh ạ̉nạ ạ̉kwn mn gẖyrk ạ̹nt dạ ạ̹nt ḥmạyty wsr ạ̉mạny
 1- lyh mạnạdtsẖ bdry ʿlyk bạhrb bs mnk lyk
 sạkn jwh ḥbẗ qlbk lkn qlby qạsy ʿlyk
 2- kẖạyf jwạk btkẖbyny tạyh ạ̹ydyk rạḥ thdyyny
 rwḥy mʿạk mrtạḥẗ yạrby ạ̉ṭlb tʿṭf tmly̱ ymyny
 3- ḥbk ṭʿm wmʿny̱ ḥyạty lyk ạlqlb wkl ṣlạty
 kẖyrk kẖḍr ạ̉rḍy ạlbwr ạ̹nt yạrby wjwdy wdẖạty</lyrics>
